com.github.dm.jrt.core.builder

Interface ChannelBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelConfigurable<ChannelBuilder>, ChannelConfiguration.Configurable<ChannelBuilder>

    public interface ChannelBuilder
extends ChannelConfigurable<ChannelBuilder>
    Interface defining a builder of channel objects.

    Note that the passed inputs might be delivered through the configured runner.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 03/07/2015.
